name: SkyRocket (Dackss)
description:
Your friend told you to meet them at the top of Wintry mountain to watch the fireworks. They also left some fireworks to help you boost to the top faster. Now you must run and jump your way through 10 screens of 2D-Platforming to reach the top in time for new years. 

--Controls--

WASD (or arrow keys) to move

W or Up arrow to double jump with the rocket

--Credits--

Art, Code and Music by Dackss 

Sound effects made with jsfxr
